description: Tequila is the alter ego to Kahlua. She is different than Kahlua in most regards. For one, while Kahlua cannot effectively utilize all of her magical powers, Tequila can. Tequila also has bright-purple hair as opposed to Kahlua`s blond hair. Overall, Tequila`s character is much different. For example, she is much more daring, aggressive, and hot-headed than Kahlua.
name: Tequila Marjoram
